her own ringtone--

96
00:03:49,673 --> 00:03:51,257
"Bernadette,"
by The Four Tops.

97
00:03:51,258 --> 00:03:52,975
Hello, Bernadette.

98
00:03:54,211 --> 00:03:57,863
