finding a girl on my own.

137
00:05:17,093 --> 00:05:19,145
Oh, Leonard, you remind me

138
00:05:19,146 --> 00:05:21,313
of the funny old story
about a man

139
00:05:21,314 --> 00:05:23,299
who walks into a women's
correctional institution

140
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:24,650
with a stack of paperwork

141
00:05:24,651 --> 00:05:27,186
that will allow
the female convicts to go free.

142
00:05:27,187 --> 00:05:29,088
You're saying I
couldn't get laid

143
00:05:29,089 --> 00:05:32,608
