164
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,686
what all the hoopla's about.

165
00:06:17,687 --> 00:06:19,488
Go on, Amy.

166
00:06:19,489 --> 00:06:21,257
From a neurobiological
standpoint, Leonard,

167
00:06:21,258 --> 00:06:23,759
