because your psychological state

168
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:26,228
is causing
an actual pheromone-based stink

169
00:06:26,229 --> 00:06:27,880
of desperation.

170
00:06:28,899 --> 00:06:30,049
Did you know that, Leonard?

171
00:06:30,050 --> 00:06:31,800
No.
I did.

172
00:06:33,336 --> 00:06:35,237
I understand
that some people find mates

173
00:06:35,238 --> 00:06:37,706
