193
00:07:23,119 --> 00:07:27,156
He's a cornucopia
of social awkwardness.

194
00:07:27,157 --> 00:07:28,524
Cornucopia.

195
00:07:28,525 --> 00:07:29,558
What a mellifluous word.

196
00:07:29,559 --> 00:07:31,410
Let's make that our word
of the day.

197
00:07:31,411 --> 00:07:34,597
Agreed. And we'll use
mellifluous tomorrow.

198
00:07:34,598 --> 00:07:37,399
Well, I have to void my bladder.

199
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:39,685
It was nice spending this time
with you.

200
00:07:39,686 --> 00:07:41,053
