214
00:08:08,264 --> 00:08:11,216
Amy Farrah Fowler has asked me
to meet her mother.

215
00:08:11,217 --> 00:08:12,418
Yeah. So?

216
00:08:12,419 --> 00:08:15,104
What does that mean?

217
00:08:15,105 --> 00:08:17,056
Well, you know
how you're always saying

218
00:08:17,057 --> 00:08:19,308
that Amy is a girl
who's your friend,

219
00:08:19,309 --> 00:08:20,476
